    F --> F2[No]
    F --> F999[Unclear]

    F1 --> FYes{Count:Q15-1}
    F2 --> FNo{Count:Q15-0}

    F2 & F999 --> G{Q16}
    G & F1 --> G1[Yes] %% If previous question is yes, this one is scored yes. %%
    G --> G2[No]
    G --> G999[Unclear]

    G1 --> GYes{Count:Q16-1}
    G2 --> GNo{Count:Q16-0}

    B1 & B2 & B3 & B4 & B5 & B6 & B7 & B8 --> H{Q17}
    H --> H1[Yes]
    H --> H2[No]
    H --> H999[Unclear]

