    H2 --> HNo{Count:Q17-0}

    B3 --> IA{Q18A} %% Specific Q1uestion for employed ppl %%
    B4 --> IB{Q18B} %% Specific Q1uestion for studying ppl %%
    B5 --> IC{Q18C}
    B6 & B7 & B8 --> ID{Q18D}
    B1 & B2 & IA & IB & IC & ID --> I1[Negative]
    IA & IB & IC & ID --> I2[Inconsistent]
    IA & IB & IC & ID --> I3[Unrewarding]
    IA & IB & IC & ID --> I3[Positive]
    IA & IB & IC & ID --> I999[Unclear]

    I1 --> I-S0{Count:Q18-S0}
    I2 --> I-S1{Count:Q18-S1}
    I3 --> I-S2{Count:Q18-S2}
    I4 --> I-S3{Count:Q18-S3}

    B3 --> JA{Q19A} %% Specific Question for employed ppl %%
    B4 --> JB{Q19B} %% Specific Question for studying ppl %%
    B5 --> JC{Q19C} %% Specific Question for studying and working ppl %%
    B1 & B2 & JA & JB & JC --> J1[Problematic]
    JA & JB & JC --> J2[Nonconstructive]
    JA & JB & JC --> J3[Respectful]
    JA & JB & JC --> J3[Positive]
    JA & JB & JC --> J999[Unclear]

    J1 --> J-S0{Count:Q19-S0}
    J2 --> J-S1{Count:Q19-S1}
    J3 --> J-S2{Count:Q19-S2}
    J4 --> J-S3{Count:Q19-S3}

    B3 --> KA{Q20A} %% Specific Question for employed ppl %%
    B4 --> KB{Q20B} %% Specific Question for studying ppl %%
    B5 --> KC{Q20C} %% Specific Question for studying and working ppl %%
